data.description: Welcome to this 2021-built, resplendent residence in Sugarmill Woods, a coveted community offering privacy and tranquility. This elegant home, set on a spacious .29-acre plot with no rear neighbors, is an oasis of luxury and comfort. Four bedrooms, three bathrooms, and an office elegantly unfold across a split floor plan. Park in style in a three-car garage and step onto vinyl wood flooring that extends throughout the main living areas. A gourmet kitchen forms the heart of the home, showcasing granite countertops, smart appliances, and a pantry. The adjoining sunny eat-in space presents calming vistas of the private, wooded backyard. High ceilings and crown molding grace the dining and living rooms, while abundant windows lets in the natural light. The large master suite is a private retreat, complete with tray ceilings, crown molding, an ensuite bathroom featuring a dual sink vanity, granite counters, and a large shower and a spacious walk-in closet. This treasure, nestled in the Cypress Village of Sugarmill Woods, offers 2 18-hole golf courses and a restaurant with optional membership packages. With Homosassa River State Wildlife Park, and the Gulf of Mexico just 25 minutes away, discover a world where the enchanting play of mermaids and manatees becomes your everyday reality. Close to an array of shops, restaurants, Suncoast Parkway, and tourist attractions, this gem of a home is awaiting its new owner. Arrange your private showing today and seize this opportunity before it slips away.
